# HTTP and Environment Conventions

- Use the shared axios client: [axiosInstance.ts](mdc:wy-frontend/src/lib/axiosInstance.ts).
- Do not create ad-hoc fetch/axios instances in components.
- Configure API base URL and secrets via `.env.local`; do not hardcode URLs.
- Centralize error handling and interceptors in the shared axios instance.
- Prefer typed responses aligned with backend Pydantic schemas.

Examples and references:
- Client: [axiosInstance.ts](mdc:wy-frontend/src/lib/axiosInstance.ts)
- Types: colocate `types.ts` in the feature directory (e.g., `src/app/retreats/types.ts`).
